{"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Checkbox is a UI element that allows to select multiple options from a set of mutually non exclusive choices."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Checkbox that does not show icon or text, provides greater flexibility when creating other components that require a checkbox to be displayed."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"indeterminate","type":"text"}]},{"text":": like a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In you are looking for a checkbox with only two possible values, refer to "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","text":"Cases forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Suggestions","text":"Suggestions"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","type":"reference","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unified-design-system.orange.com"}],"overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"O